headline: ROLLINS, INC. SCHEDULES DATE FOR RELEASE OF FIRST QUARTER 2025 FINANCIAL RESULTS
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, today announced that it will release its first quarter results for the period ended March 31, 2025, after the market closes on Wednesday, April 23, 2025. In conjunction with its release, the Company will host a conference call to review the Company's financial and operating results before the market opens on Thursday, April 24, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
